premise_source_doc_sentence: The Promise is the fourth studio album by the classical crossover group , Il Divo.The Promise was released globally on November 10 , 2008 , except in the US and Canada , where it was released November 17 , Ireland and Mexico where it was released on November 7 , and Japan , on 26 November .
